Package: recPhyloParse
Type: Package
Title: Parse RecPhyloXML Files
Version: 0.3.0
Author: person("Federico", "Marotta", email = "federico.marotta@embl.de",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Federico Marotta <federico.marotta@embl.de>
Description: Imports reconciliated phylogenetic trees (recPhyloXML) as R6
    objects and converts them to `data.frame`s. All the attributes and
    coordinates needed for plotting the trees are calculated, so that standard
    ggplot2 geoms can be used.
URL: https://github.com/fmarotta/recPhyloParse
BugReports: https://github.com/fmarotta/recPhyloParse/issues
Imports:
    xml2,
    R6
Suggests:
    covr,
    ggplot2,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    vdiffr
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Config/testthat/edition: 3
